<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Romans_et_nouvelles">Romans et nouvelles</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Anatole_France&amp;veaction=edit&amp;section=13" class="mw-editsection-visualeditor" title="Modifier la section : Romans et nouvelles">modifier</a><span class="mw-editsection-divider"> | </span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Anatole_France&amp;action=edit&amp;section=13" title="Modifier la section : Romans et nouvelles">modifier le code</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
