<h3><span id="Critique_litt.C3.A9raire"></span><span class="mw-headline" id="Critique_littéraire">Critique littéraire</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Anatole_France&amp;veaction=edit&amp;section=17" class="mw-editsection-visualeditor" title="Modifier la section : Critique littéraire">modifier</a><span class="mw-editsection-divider"> | </span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Anatole_France&amp;action=edit&amp;section=17" title="Modifier la section : Critique littéraire">modifier le code</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
